description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personal Assistant to the Network Associate Medical Directors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;12 month fixed term post (maybe extended on review) providing administrative and PA function to the locality medical leads. Given the nature of this role, it will be aligned directly to the Medical Directorate where line management will reside. However, working from other bases and home can be supported.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You need to be an organised, dynamic, and proactive individual who can manage diaries and support a number of individuals across the organisation. You will have a proven track record of working well with others and the ability to manage your time effectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Dr Mark Worthington on 07779 455853 or mark.worthington@lancashirecare.nhs.uk to discuss this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
